              <p>I developed a structured localisation methodology: a flexible framework with core principles and adaptable components. I ran workshops with top five priority markets, tested and evolved the approach. This <strong>accelerated readiness, reduced ambiguity,</strong> and ensured the service was culturally, clinically, and operationally relevant in each market.</p>
            </div>
