              <h4>Operationalising and scaling the service</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar-content">
            <div class="pillar-text">
              <p>A service of this scale requires more than design. It requires the capability to sustain it.</p>
              <p>Working with the central RLT teams, I built the <strong>operational backbone</strong> for long-term success. It includes prioritisation and governance framework, a repeatable implementation toolkit and a comprehensive package to onboard new markets rapidly.</p>
              <p>This transformed the organisation's readiness from theoretical to operational, establishing the people, processes, and tools required to scale RLT consistently across the globe.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-image">
              <ImageCarousel
                images={pillar4Images.map((img, i) => ({
                  src: img.src,
                  srcset: img.srcSet.attribute,
                  alt: i === 0 ? "Operational toolkits" : "Capability building frameworks",
                  width: img.attributes.width,
                  height: img.attributes.height
